T02TD3382E:53b-1: ma h'a pra tyam g'i ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD3382E:53b-3: phyir bzlog ma chen mo'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3382E:53b-4: 'phags ma phyir bzlog ma chen mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3382E:53b-5: phyir bzlog ma chen mo nag mo zhal gcig phyag drug mar 'dod do //
T02TD3382E:53b-8: mchog sbyin pa ni g-yas kyi phyag go //
T02TD3382E:54a-1: gnas pa'i zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub dang ldan pa ni g-yon pa'i phyag go //
T02TD3382E:54a-3: mi bskyod pas dbu brgyan pa'o //
T02TD3382E:54a-4: lha rdzas kyi na bza' dang /
T02TD3382E:54a-5: rgyan dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor ma zhes bya ba la sogs pa'o //
T02TD3382E:54a-8: phyir bzlog pa chen mo'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3382E:54a-9: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3382E:54a-10: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o//
